$ matching the best known lower bound for any explicit\ntensor in three dimensions over $GF(2)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2018 16:35:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Apr 2018 02:40:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-26"}
