he HOOI execution time by a\nfactor of up to 3x. On the other hand, its distribution time is comparable to\nthe prior lightweight schemes and is typically lesser than the execution time\nof a single HOOI iteration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Apr 2018 11:59:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Jan 2020 00:47:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
